\begin_layout Abstract
In this document I provide an update on the commissioning of setup for the
 long term studies of irradiated LGAD detectors at UZH.
 This setup is intended to periodically monitor the characteristics and
 performance of irradiated LGAD detectors while they are kept constantly
 biased for a long period of time.
 
\end_layout

